    21→* Rewrite README to get humans started more quickly with less noise while simultaneously making more accessible for llms and agents to go deeper into details.
    23→## [17.2.4](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/compare/v17.2.3...v17.2.4) (2026-02-05)
