    48→## [17.2.0](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/compare/v17.1.0...v17.2.0) (2025-07-09)
    49→
    50→### Added
    51→
    52→* Optionally specify `DOTENV_CONFIG_QUIET=true` in your environment or `.env` file to quiet the runtime log ([#889](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/pull/889))
    53→* Just like dotenv any `DOTENV_CONFIG_` environment variables take precedence over any code set options like `({quiet: false})`
